sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant M as Main
    participant A as Algorithms
    participant HM as HashMap

    U->>M: Run program
    M->>A: twoSum(nums, target)
    A->>HM: new HashMap()
    HM-->>A: empty map
    loop for i = 0 to n-1
        A->>A: complement = target - nums[i]
        A->>HM: containsKey(complement)
        alt found
            HM-->>A: true
            A-->>M: [seen[complement], i]
            M-->>U: Result
        else not found
            HM-->>A: false
            A->>HM: put(nums[i], i)
        end
    end
    A-->>M: NoSuchElementException
    M-->>U: Error

    Note over A,HM: O(n) time, O(n) space
